 _______________________________________________________________________

 Mandriva Linux Security Advisory                         MDVSA-2014:093
 http://www.mandriva.com/en/support/security/
 _______________________________________________________________________

 Package : couchdb
 Date    : May 16, 2014
 Affected: Business Server 1.0
 _______________________________________________________________________

 Problem Description:

 Updated couchdb packages fix security vulnerability:
 
 Apache CouchDB 1.5.0 and earlier allows remote attackers to cause a
 denial of service (CPU and memory consumption) via the count parameter
 to /_uuids (CVE-2014-2668).
 _______________________________________________________________________

 References:

 http://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2014-2668
 http://advisories.mageia.org/MGASA-2014-0203.html
 _______________________________________________________________________

